com.ekito.simpleKML.model

Class Update

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ekito.simpleKML.model.Update

  • public class Update
extends java.lang.Object
    Specifies an addition, change, or deletion to KML data that has already been loaded using the specified URL. The targetHref specifies the .kml or .kmz file whose data (within Google Earth) is to be modified. Update is always contained in a NetworkLinkControl. Furthermore, the file containing the NetworkLinkControl must have been loaded by a NetworkLink.
